                <p>Tuscany is a residential community found in northwest Calgary. This community was established in 1994 and since then, has become the residence for more than 19,000 people near the western side of Calgary.</p>
                <p>One of the larger communities in the area, Tuscany is full of a variety of fun and interesting things that makes living here relaxing and convenient. Most prominently, the area has a large amount of green space, which is filled with playgrounds and sports fields, so no matter what age you are, there is always something to do.</p>
                <p>Tuscany offers many stores and restaurants that are easily accessible via the well-designed roads. All you have to do is take a short walk to the central Tuscany Market shopping complex and you will find various amenities such as a bank, grocery stores and restaurants.</p>
                <p>Tuscany also boasts an impressive variety of homes from standalone housing as well as larger condominiums and apartments that are perfect for affordable living. Also, with easy access to the rest of the city via Highway 1A, you won't have to worry about your daily commute taking too long.</p>
                <p>A great addition to any community is the space for recreational activities and sports. Tuscany provides this valuable infrastructure in the form of a community club and outdoor ice-skating rink located near the centre of the neighbourhood. So, you can spend a day with friends ice skating and having fun within the community itself.</p>
